{"tid":619152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【打工皇帝】霍建寧日薪57萬等於打工仔逾3年人工","createTime":"2018-04-06T11:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T12:58:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"54fb9ae29193d6aa9a809e00a047a9d1b2ffa84d","tid":619152,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"長和(001)最新年報顯示，素有「打工皇帝」之稱的長和聯席董事總經理霍建寧，去年總酬金達2.1億，其中酌情花紅達1.97億，以全年365日計，日薪達57.6萬，據政府2016年本港工作人口（不包括外籍家庭傭工）的月入中位數1.55萬元水平，即要港人工作超過3年，才能追得上打工皇帝的日薪。<br />\n<br />\n2016年多隻藍籌股盈利表現，雖有受到經濟放緩所拖累，多位高層紛紛需要減人工，霍建寧全年總薪酬亦按年減少4.6%，至去年經濟復蘇，霍建寧的人工並亦由2億升至2.1億，升幅達4.8%，多逾1千萬人工，但仍未追及2015年的2.15億。"},{"pid":"227d699e2e472c2bdbce3bbc5315fa9940117ef5","tid":619152,"uid":50667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"每返2日就俾到首期，返20日就買到一個單位。"},{"pid":"fe8a53b3642fbced4ede4f9bc6a4d4c2c5aa725b","tid":619152,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"227d699e2e472c2bdbce3bbc5315fa9940117ef5","tid":619152,"uid":50667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"每返2日就俾到首期，返20日就買到一個單位。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"計埋放假排第一都要差唔多成個月先買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b76e2e56d84c062dafc52b7128201c2cc5c5ae","tid":619152,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"留明睇連登仔話生不逢時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edda9d84598621cde17fdbbc99708ccfa9362d0","tid":619152,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fe8a53b3642fbced4ede4f9bc6a4d4c2c5aa725b","tid":619152,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"227d699e2e472c